<h2><strong>How to Prepare A Luxury Car For Collector Car Shipping?</strong></h2>
Here are some steps to prepare your luxury car for collector car shipping:
<ul>
 	<li>Please ensure the car is cleaned inside and outside with great attention to detail. This will help prevent any dirt or debris from causing damage while shipping.</li>
 	<li>Please inspect the car thoroughly to identify any pre-existing damage. Kindly note any dents, scratches, or other blemishes on the item, as it is important to document them for the shipping company.</li>
 	<li>Please take photographs of the car from every possible angle. This documentation may be helpful in any damage that occurs during shipping.</li>
 	<li>Deactivate any car alarm systems that may have been installed. This will help prevent any possible problems with the alarm being triggered during transportation.</li>
 	<li>Ensure that the fuel tank contains an ample amount of fuel. A full gas tank can protect the engine if encountering rough roads while shipping.</li>
